{"tid":1755312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一場小勝 就沖昏頭昏腦 就嚟輸啦 !!!!!","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:06:10.000Z","uid":186492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdeb1ee84800a1dbfb343af12ea03499c80af7e","tid":1755312,"uid":186492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"我都唔想屌大家。<br />\n<br />\n我知道，尋日區選大勝，係好開心，係證明左民心所向。<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家核爆都唔割𥱊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記，這些成果唔係個天跌落嚟。係由六月到今日，各方手足用血汗同淚水換返嚟。有咁結果係好合情理。難聽啲講句，等價交換嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n休息左成日，我到依家都仲未見到有活動post。我想問，大家係咪覺得贏咗區選就好滿意。其他訴求就唔需要再爭取？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請大家推返活動post! </span></span>講下文宣野！大家自high少陣得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad59d1410c659863d9ef2aa47ed3e596d6c0808","tid":1755312,"uid":318670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396587077872965fd5186638065fb89d884178cd","tid":1755312,"uid":204689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9056052cce05790f448b39be079a0e21957a743e","tid":1755312,"uid":204689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc70c72a3014e3b893cfedbbe55718a844e3f574","tid":1755312,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔好再j區選同梁凱晴，做返正經野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f348f94f6431ec957ba7345bfd927958779551","tid":1755312,"uid":186492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"推多一推"},{"pid":"85fdad9958c810c5fe705d11e38e0018545a84b4","tid":1755312,"uid":186492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"推多次"},{"pid":"3f6970abb10a9584ba35b7fe615bd86563220a26","tid":1755312,"uid":186492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"推x3"},{"pid":"3c520093dd8d38333301c860e76fd59bc252a8d2","tid":1755312,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}